The Devil and Daniel Johnston;;91;;88;;PG-13;;Filmmaker Jeff Feuerzeig chronicles the life of a manic-depressive musician and artist, using a blend of home movies, Johnston's own audiotapes, vintage performances and current footage. Johnston has recorded more than 10 full-length albums and amassed a prolific portfolio of sketches, and has among his supporters Matt Groening, David Bowie, Sonic Youth, Beck, and Tom Waits.;;Documentary;;Jeff Feuerzeig;;2006;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1158179-devil_and_daniel_johnston